title: Don’t miss the music at this year’s State Fair
text: Don’t miss the music at this year’s State Fair Don’t miss the music at this year’s State Fair Advocate staff photo by STACY GILL -- The Gillis Silo, pictured here performing in Zachary, will play some rockin' country at 8 p.m. Saturday, Oct. 31 at the Greater Baton Rouge State Fair. Advocate staff photo by HEATHER MCCLELLAND -- James Linden Hogg performs at the Greater Baton Rouge State Fair at 6 p.m. Tuesday, Oct. 27. Photo provided by Jeanne McCollister -- Werewolf, an 80s cover band, performs at 8:30 p.m. Friday, Oct. 30 at the Greater Baton Rouge State Fair. ADVOCATE STAFF REPORT
